For multiple region 
we have to create a alias so we can assign the Ec2 while creating 
eg-
provider "aws" {
 alias      = "ap-south-1"
  region     = "ap-south-1"
and 
 alias      = "ap-northeast-3"
  region     = "ap-northeast-3"



and also we add secret key for them
eg 
provider "aws" {
 alias      = "ap-south-1"
  region     = "ap-south-1"
  access_key = "AKIAWELPQ*****6NADSO"
  secret_key = "pJ****************HLp"
